trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanging" /> event, <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosing" /> event, and <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleting" /> event.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o evento <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanging" />, o evento <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosing" /> e o evento <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleting" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventArgs> class contains information for several different Web Parts events that can be canceled.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventArgs> classe contém informações para vários eventos diferentes de Web Parts que podem ser cancelados.

trans-unit.source: These events include the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanging>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosing>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleting> events.
trans-unit.target: Esses eventos incluem a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanging>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosing>, e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleting> eventos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventArgs> class provides access to the Web Parts control involved in the event.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventArgs> classe fornece acesso para o controle de Web Parts envolvido no evento.

trans-unit.source: The Web Parts control is accessed through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventArgs.WebPart%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O controle de Web Parts é acessado por meio de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventArgs.WebPart%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> (or server or user control) involved in the event.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> (ou controle de servidor ou usuário) envolvido no evento.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCancelEventArgs" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the Web Parts control involved in the cancelable event.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o controle de Web Parts envolvido no evento cancelável.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> involved in a <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanging" />, <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosing" />, or <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleting" /> event.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart" /> envolvidos em uma <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanging" />, <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosing" />, ou <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleting" /> eventos.
